  "bio_raw": "Rezwana Islam has completed CELTA (The Certificate in English Language Teaching to Adults) as a part of Cambridge English Language Assessment, part of the University of Cambridge. She has 5 years' experience as a TESOL trainer in different educational institutions. Her experience as an IELTS trainer at British Council has enabled her to explore different areas of skill development.\nShe is currently teaching at the Center for Language Studies (CLS), University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB).",
  "stated_interests": [
    "TESOL, Developing learner autonomy, Feedback and Error Correction, academic writing, Medium of instruction, interest and expertise in IELTS"
